dc_title_s: Geologic map of the Antioch South & Brentwood quadrangles, Contra Costa County, California
dc_description_s: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch. Relief shown by contours and spot heights. "Nicholas Lloyd Taliaferro Memorial Map." "Topographic base map from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle Antioch South, CA 1953, DMA 1659 IV NE - Series V895, Photorevised 1980; Brentwood, CA 1978, AMS 1659 I NW - Series V895." "First printing, February 2006." "Contour interval Antioch South quadrangle 20 feet ; Brentwood quadrangle 20 and 5 feet." Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology. Includes "pertinent references."
dc_publisher_s: Santa Barbara Museum of Natural History
